snippet.title: BHunter - unique overview of all districts
snippet.description:
BHunter was released by Midas in 1999 and its size is less than 7 MB.
All districts shown in order as they appear during game progression:
0:00 - Centre
0:18 - Bronx
0:30 - City Ring
0:59 - Stadium
1:20 - Chinatown
1:30 - Industrial district
1:49 - Financial district
2:12 - Harbour
2:40 - Spaceport
3:20 - New Vegas
3:38 - Sewers
4:06 - Mines
Thanks for watching.
